description:
Unravel the lost history of WUCHANG: Fallen Feathers in the new Lore Trailer.

The avians defied fate, bending the threads of causality to escape death itself. But destiny could not be undone.

A war erupted, fracturing reality and scattering relics of power across the land. The survivors sought refuge among mortals, but their past could not be buried forever.

Launching day one on Game Pass and Xbox Series X|S in 2025.
